Document:     ggivtk

Purpose:      Python module implementing the VtkField Ggi element for pygipsy.

Category:     SYSTEM

File:         ggivtk.src

Author:       J.P. Terlouw

Description:  ggivtk is a pre-compiled module which augments the
              standard Python module gipsy. It implements the _VtkField
              class and a factory method for _Container.

Use:          The module is automatically imported by the gipsy module.

Updates:      Jul 18, 2007: JPT, Document created.
              Feb 28, 2010: JPT, added -fPIC switch to compilations
              Sep  3, 2012: JPT, conditional code for different VTK versions
